# Vendored go-unifi Codegen

This directory contains code vendored from
[filipowm/go-unifi](https://github.com/filipowm/go-unifi).

**DO NOT EDIT THESE FILES MANUALLY**

## Source

- Repository: https://github.com/filipowm/go-unifi
- License: MPL-2.0
- Version: See `../../.go-unifi-version`

## Updating

To update to a new version:

1. Update `.go-unifi-version` with the new tag
2. Run `task sync-go-unifi`
